<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200915/b6e0b8a079da416aa72adaa646cc6610.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清饮一杯茶，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这需要多复杂呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烧开一壶水，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">洗净三杯两盏，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">泡透一撮茶，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吹扬热气，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浅浅品味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200915/e42cfe3f954c4a55aec6f4f05c8e4ab3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">繁芜错杂的世间，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总有些人简单随性，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">总有些灵魂散着芳香，</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
